YOU: Tell me about your husband. What sort of a man was he?

DUCHESS: He was an exceptionally kind man. I experienced the human emotion of love towards him, which was one of several factors leading to our marriage. Additionally, he was one hundred and eighty-one centimetres in height, he had gray hair, and he was assigned to the male gender.

